name: The Original Poem for the song "Dunce" by Non-Adjective
description:
This is an poem hand-written while on the clock in Springfield, MO.

Scribbled in 2018.

Buy this and I will either ship you the physical poem, or post a video of me destroying it. Just DM me on Twitter after your purchase and show me proof (Tezos Proiles). 14 days after purchase, if I don't hear from you, I will destroy the photo anyways.
